creator: Hamilton Wright Mabie
description:
LibriVox recording of Young Folks' Treasury, Volume 2 by Hamilton Wright Mabie.
Read in English by Lynne Thompson; ElleyKat; Greg Giordano; Ellen Preckel; Katalina Watt; Arnie Horton; thestorygirl; drakaunus; Bill Boerst; Sarah Alaine Swart; Julia Niedermaier; rookieblue; Claudia Salto; Kate Zdepski; Ernst Pattynama; tealrobin; Jill Engle; luckyemma; Ravi Shankar; Alexander Hatton; constatine; Mike Pelton; Chill28; Marty; Kathy Wright; Jacki Horn
This is the second book in a twelve volume series, and highlights myths and legendary heroes from around the world, from Ancient Greece to Scandinavia and the Far East. They are aimed at the junior audience. (Summary by Lynne Thompson)
For further information, including links to M4B audio book, online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
